installation.html.body:
Installation
NPM 5
npm install ng-snotify
yarn
yarn add ng-snotify
Import Module
Import SnotifyModule, also you can try SnotifyModule.forRoot() if you have build errorsAnd provide SnotifyService with default configuration object  

How to change ToastDefaults config - options  

// Import your library
import { SnotifyModule, SnotifyService, ToastDefaults } from 'ng-snotify';

@NgModule({
  imports: [
    BrowserModule,
    SnotifyModule
  ],
  providers: [
    { provide: 'SnotifyToastConfig', useValue: ToastDefaults},
    SnotifyService
  ]
})
export class AppModule { }

Add selector
Include ng-snotify component to you root component


Dependency injection
Now you should inject SnotifyService
import {SnotifyService} from 'ng-snotify';

@Component({
  selector: 'app-root',
  templateUrl: './app.component.html',
  styleUrls: ['./app.component.css']
})
export class AppComponent {
  constructor(private snotifyService: SnotifyService) {}
}

Import Styles
